{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355420/extras/Steam_600x73.png?t=1651593537\" /><br>Pixboy, a mad scientist, finally found a recipe for an ultimate potion. However, malicious dogs destroyed his dreams. Time for revenge!<br><strong>Feel the retro vibes, travel back to the past, enjoy chunky pixels and chiptune music!</strong><br><br><strong>Be agile!</strong><br>Run, jump, soar and avoid deadly obstacles. Don't give up! You will succeed... eventually.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355420/extras/pixboy_600x200_cyber_run_60fps_3.gif?t=1651593537\" /><br><br><br><strong>Leave no one behind!</strong><br>Defeat enemies using your super-duper-powerful slingshot. Out of ammo? Jump on foes' heads to defeat them and to get extra bullet!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355420/extras/pixboy_600x200_forest_lvl5_3.gif?t=1651593537\" /><br>(If you feel like a pacifist, spare all the enemies on level and get a special <strong>Pacifist Badge</strong>! But beware: won't be easy!)<br><br><br><strong>Seek for secrets!</strong> <br>Find 'Em all! It's a piece of cake, really...<br>Only 150 secret rooms. Good luck :)<br>Small hint: <span class=\"bb_spoiler\">look for different patterns on walls</span><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355420/extras/pixboy_600x200_snowland_secret.gif?t=1651593537\" /><br><br><br><strong>Meet strange creatures!</strong><br>There are 30 of them. <br>So for now, meet the Fluffy. Fluffy is full of surprises, figuratively and literally.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355420/extras/pixboy_600x200_forest_fluffy_4.gif?t=1651593537\" /><br><br><br><strong>Tease your mind!</strong><br>Each jump - every mechanism rotates.